This topic explains how to install <%= vars.platform_name %> on Microsoft Azure manually.

To install <%= vars.platform_name %> on Azure manually, do the following:

1. Deploy Pivotal Operations Manager. See [Deploying Ops Manager on Azure](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.','-') %>/azure/deploy-manual.html).

1. Configure BOSH Director. See [Configuring BOSH Director on Azure](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.','-') %>/azure/config-manual.html).

